# Learning Vulkan w SDL3 
repo to store files while learning vulkan w SDL3

# Building

need these packages, note this if for fedora, other distros may be named different

```
dnf install \
    libX11-devel libXext-devel libXrandr-devel libXcursor-devel \
    libXfixes-devel libXi-devel libXScrnSaver-devel libXtst-devel \
    wayland-devel libdecor-devel mesa-libGL-devel mesa-libEGL-devel \
    xorg-x11-server-devel
```

and these i guess idk

```
dnf install dbus-devel pipewire-devel pulseaudio-libs-devel libusb1-devel systemd-devel
```

1. Create and enter a build directory
    - `cmake -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug`
2. Compile the project
    - `cmake --build build`
3. Run
    - `./build/Debug/hello`

